            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-4190aed0-0b3a-4157-a5c1-6108871f6b2d">
                Captain Hewitson  (Hull. Central)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-4190aed0-0b3a-4157-a5c1-6108871f6b2d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
