<p class="">That is what the Lord Chancellor said.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-19b2d68c-6171-4f92-9b93-a6b7f3301991" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
