            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-64293389-26ff-42c2-820e-6309d1c98079">
                Mr. Macmillan
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-64293389-26ff-42c2-820e-6309d1c98079" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
