land, Sir Richard</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Field, Capt. W. J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>MacColl, J. E.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Adams, Richard</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Finch, H. J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McGhee, H. G</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Albu, A. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Fletcher, E. G. M. (Islington, E.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McGovern, J.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Allen, A. C. (Bosworth)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Follick, M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McInnes, J</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Allen, Scholefield (Crewe)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Foot, M. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mack, J. D.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Anderson, A. (Motherwell)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Forman, J. C.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McKay, J. (Wallsend)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Anderson, F. (Whitehaven)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Fraser, T. (Hamilton)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mackay, R. W. G. (Reading, N.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Attlee, Rt. Hon. C. R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Freeman, J, (Watford)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McLeavy, F.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Awbery, S. S.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Freeman, Peter (Newport)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>MacMillan, M. K. (Western Isles)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Ayles, W. H.</td></p><p class="Division"