        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-45e0ecf3-8a2c-4bb9-b9d4-38f9ecd7d37d'>
            
<p class="">Main Question put, and agreed to.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
